headline: AI For Impact Day welcomes Dell Technologies as platinum sponsor
summary: Agile Defense announced today that Dell Technologies has joined its AI for Impact Day event as the platinum sponsor. The one-day summit takes place on June 26 in Reston, VA. Participants will explore real-world applications of AI and data solutions to optimize government, improve operational efficiency and support mission critical tasks.

headline: Dell Technologies (NYSE:DELL) Partners With Trend Micro And NVIDIA For AI Security Solutions
summary: Dell Technologies (NYSE:DELL) has made significant strides in innovation with its recent collaboration with Trend Micro and NVIDIA, launching secure, AI-powered infrastructure solutions. This initiative, combined with the company's consistent dividend payout and share buyback programs, aligns well with shareholder interests. During the past quarter, Dell's 17% price increase also benefitted from positive market sentiments, as broader indices experienced modest gains amid geopolitical tensions...
